  "description": [
    "EDITORIAL COMMENT According to the secretary of the Protestant Epis copal board of missions the future relations of Japan will be not to instruct the Americans in warfare but in the true beauty of religion He sees a day when Japan shall embrace Christianity and uniting with it their innate courtesy shall become in turn the teacher of those who taught them We begin to feel some charity for apparent police incompetence in provincial places when we learn that in Washington which has every facility for an ap proximately perfect police system violence and rob bery have lately become frequent on the open streets Its usual form is the knocking down and robbery of women Since the last of dctolcr the papers have reported some twenty occurrences of the kind For some months in many parts of the country there has been a reawakening of that fearfully de moralizing form of terror which is aroused by the mysterious and deadly activity of such secret organi zations as the Italian Maffia This time it is the so called Black Hand also of Italian origin To this hand is attributed the many otherwise inexplicable crimes of blackmail kidnapping bombthrowing and fiendish murder"
  ],
